text: Chulpan () is a rural locality (a village) in Tarkazinsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 12 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 50 km from Yermekeyevo, 7 km from Tarkazy. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Chulpan, Yermekeyevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
